nodes.text: The Old Trade Federation Route was a hyperspace route once used by the Trade Federation. It passed through the planet Naboo in the Mid Rim's Chommell sector.

The Old Trade Federation Route was first mentioned in the new Star Wars canon in Rise of the Separatists, a 2019 supplement to Fantasy Flight Games' series of Star Wars roleplaying products. It was originally created for the Star Wars Legends continuity, where it first appeared in Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed, a 2004 expansion to the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies.
